 Reporter|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108115018/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wga-writers-guild-awards-winners-list-292639|archive-date=January 8, 2020|access-date=January 11, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" |2013\n|Golden Globe Awards\n|Best Actress \u2014 Television Series Musical or Comedy\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"goldenglobes.com\" />\n|-\n|[[Screen Actors Guild]]\n|[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/sag-awards-2013-complete-list-415699|title=SAG Awards 2013: Complete List of Winners|last=THR Staff|first=|date=January 27, 2013|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190322114003/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/sag-awards-2013-complete-list-415699|archive-date=March 22, 2019|access-date=2019-11-04}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Writers Guild of America\n|[[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Comedy Series|Television: Comedy Series]]\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"Writers Guild Award Winners\">{{Cite web|url=https://awards.wga.org/awards/nominees-winners/2018-2013|title=Writers Guild Awards Winners 2019-2013|last=|first=|date=|website=awards.wga.org|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530154848/https://awards.wga.org/awards/nominees-winners/2018-2013|archive-date=May 30, 2019|access-date=January 4, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Episodic Comedy|Episodic Comedy]]\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"Villarreal, Yvonne, Writers Guild\" />\n|-\n|[[Gracie Awards]]\n|Outstanding Female Actor in a Leading Role \u2013 Comedy\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://allwomeninmedia.org/gracies/2013-gracies-winners/|title=2013 Gracies Winners|last=|first=|date=|website=allwomeninmedia.org|archive-url=https://web.archive