-choice-awards-2009-nominees.html|archive-date=February 21, 2017|url-status=dead|access-date=April 13, 2019|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[MTV Movie Awards]]\n|[[MTV Movie Award for Best Jaw Dropping Moment|Best WTF Moment]]\n|rowspan=3|''Baby Mama''\n|{{won}}\n|<ref name=\"2009 MTV Movie Awards Winners\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/2009-mtv-movie-awards-winners/|title=2009 MTV Movie Awards Winners|last=|first=|date=May 31, 2009|website=/Film|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413223841/https://www.slashfilm.com/2009-mtv-movie-awards-winners/|archive-date=April 13, 2019|url-status=live|access-date=April 13, 2019|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[MTV Movie Award for Best Comedic Performance|Best Comedic Performance]]\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"2009 MTV Movie Awards Winners\" />\n|-\n|[[People's Choice Awards]]\n|Favorite On-Screen Match Up <small>(with [[Tina Fey]])</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/zap-35thpeopleschoiceawardsnominations-story.html|title=Nominees Announced for the 2009 People's Choice Awards|date=November 10, 2008|website=Chicago Tribune|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828124622/https://www.chicagotribune.com/zap-35thpeopleschoiceawardsnominations-story.html|archive-date=August 28, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Daytime Emmy Awards]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Performer In An Animated Program|Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program]]\n|rowspan=2|''The Mighty B!''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"Bierly, DAytime Emmy\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2010\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"PBS, ABC Lead 37th\" />\n|-\n|People's Choice Awards\n|Favorite TV Comedy Actress\n| rowspan=\"7\" |''Parks and Recreation''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.peopleschoice.com/pca/awards/nominees/index.jsp?year=2010|title=People's Choice Awards Nominees & Winners: 2010|date=2010|website=PeoplesChoice.com|archive-url=https://we